---
---
<section class="py-24 px-6 opacity-0" data-animate="install">
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-100">Install</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-400 mb-10">Install Ku-Ka with Homebrew in two commands.</p>

    <div class="bg-surface-50 border border-surface-200 rounded-2xl p-6 text-left font-mono text-sm">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-500 mb-4">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
          <path d="M8 9l3 3-3 3m5 0h3M5 20h14a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"/>
        </svg>
        <span>Terminal</span>
      </div>
      <code class="block text-accent-light mb-2">brew tap ChristianVilen/ku-ka</code>
      <code class="block text-accent-light">brew install --cask kuka</code>
    </div>

    <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mt-6">
      Requires macOS 13 (Ventura) or later. Or grab the <a href="https://github.com/ChristianVilen/ku-ka/releases/latest" class="text-accent-light hover:underline">.zip from GitHub Releases</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
